---
const stages = [
  "Camera / Gallery",
  "Background removal",
  "224 x 224 image",
  "RGB tensor",
  "TensorFlow Lite inference",
  "Diagnosis result"
];
---

<section id="pipeline" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Processing Pipeline</h2>
    <div class="pipeline-wrapper">
      <ol class="pipeline-diagram">
        {stages.map((stage, index) => (
          <li class="stage-item">
            <div class="stage-box">{stage}</div>
            {index < stages.length - 1 && <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true"></div>}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ol>
      <div class="technical-notes">
        <p>The model receives a 224 x 224 RGB image. Pixel values are passed in the 0-255 range because preprocessing is included inside the model.</p>
        <p>Transparent background pixels are treated as black during tensor conversion.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pipeline-wrapper {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .pipeline-diagram {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-s);
  }

  .stage-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-s);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .stage-box {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-brand);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    padding: var(--space-m);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 500;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .arrow {
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-left: 8px solid transparent;
    border-right: 8px solid transparent;
    border-top: 12px solid var(--color-brand);
    margin: var(--space-xs) 0;
  }

  .technical-notes {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--space-l);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-brand);
  }

  .technical-notes p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }

  .technical-notes p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pipeline-diagram {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: stretch;
      gap: var(--space-xs);
    }

    .stage-item {
      flex-direction: row;
      width: auto;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .stage-box {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: var(--space-m) var(--space-s);
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      height: 100%;
    }

    .arrow {
      border-top: 8px solid transparent;
      border-bottom: 8px solid transparent;
      border-left: 12px solid var(--color-brand);
      border-right: none;
      margin: 0 var(--space-xs);
    }
  }
</style>
